lead_paragraph: Japan's Sunwolves are still seeking a first Super Rugby win but head coach Mark Hammett said their performances had exceeded expectations as the country looks ahead to hosting the Rugby World Cup in 2019.

headline.print_headline: Hammett Happy With Progress of Winless Sunwolves
headline.main: Hammett Happy With Progress of Winless Sunwolves
